{"lemma":"إِبْرَةٌ","slug":"إِبْرَةٌ","root":"#.ب.ر","root_slug":"_-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29","n2402","n2410"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%A8%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"needle (all senses)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔib.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29","headword_ar":"اـِبْرَةٌ","root":"Abr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A needle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an iron"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misal~ap","text_ar":"مِسَلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":6},{"kind":"text","text":"K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibarN","text_ar":"اـِبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibaArN","text_ar":"اـِبَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity of the tail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a scorpion; (S, * M, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miy^obarN","text_ar":"مِيْبَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; of which latter the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA=biru","text_ar":"مَا=بِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A:) and of a bee. (A.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extremity"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horn. (A.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)  The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"privy"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"member"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iborapN Al*~iraAEi","text_ar":"اـِبْرَةٌ الذِّرَاعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The extremity of the elbow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj in his Khalk el-Insán; and A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremity of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAE","text_ar":"ذِرَاع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ulna"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which the measurer by the cubit measures;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) [this being always done from the extremity of the elbow;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the extremity of the bone from which the measurer by the cubit measures:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the extremity of the os humeri which is next to the elbow is called the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabiyH","text_ar":"قَبِيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuj~","text_ar":"زُجّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the elbow is between the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qbyH","text_ar":"قبيح"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Abrp Al*rAE","text_ar":"ابرة الذراع"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small bone, the head of which is large, and the rest slender, compactly joined to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qbyH","text_ar":"قبيح"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qbyH","text_ar":"قبيح"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the slender part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rAE","text_ar":"ذراع"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as in some copies of the K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small bone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(as in other copies of the K and in the M,) which latter is the right reading, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"even with the extremity of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zanod","text_ar":"زَنْد"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ulna"},{"kind":"text","text":"and to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"radius"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mn","text_ar":"من"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rAE","text_ar":"ذراع"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the extremity of the finger."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_borapu","text_ar":"الاـبْرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The bone of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"watarapu","text_ar":"وَتَرَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the heel-tendon"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a man, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the hock"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a beast], (M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is a small bone adhering to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaEob","text_ar":"كَعْب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ankle"},{"kind":"text","text":"or to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hock"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (M, TA:) and [app. more correctly “or”]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the slender part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Erqwb","text_ar":"عرقوب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hock"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the horse:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * K, * TA:) in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ErqwbAn","text_ar":"عرقوبان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or two hocks] are [what are termed]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iborataAni","text_ar":"اـِبْرَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the external extremity of each hock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b7-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miy^obarapN","text_ar":"مِيْبَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","A","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n2402","headword_ar":"ابره","root":"brh","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He adduced the evidence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K:) but as to ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barohana","text_ar":"بَرْهَنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he manifested the evidence"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is said, on the authority of IAar, to be post-classical; the former being the correct word: (AA, T, Z, Msb, TA:) or the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he adduced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did, wonderful things, and overcame men."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) Q. Q., or, as some say, Q., 1."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barohana","text_ar":"بَرْهَنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 4; and see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"brhn","text_ar":"برهن"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","AA","T","Z","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n2410","headword_ar":"اَبْرَهُ","root":"brh","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[app.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having the body in a healthy state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in good condition, after disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white in person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body and members:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but whether it have both these significations, or only the latter of them, is not clear:] fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barohaA='u","text_ar":"بَرْهَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}